Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna join our crew now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised one of my comrades something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must tend to that first \Nor I will lose face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're talking \Nabout Laboon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it. \NFranky and Robin told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! That is the name of the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is at a certain cape--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Brook! We met Laboon\Nat Twin Cape. Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked! This is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true? Did you actually meet Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been this happy in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Past! A Sad Farewell\Nwith His Cheerful Comrade!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:50.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rumbar Pirates\NMusician & Swordsman"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone! I hope you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:53.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook\N(50 years ago - Age: 38)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the day with a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... This week, Power \NTune will be presenting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the famous song, "The Black\NHandkerchief of Happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, feel free to join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ White handkerchief, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ don't let him find you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Run for it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ White handkerchief, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Don't let the octopus catch you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ That's a stain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ And now a squid is coming ♪\N--S-Stop it! Not so loud in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ There is another stain ♪\N--I'll get up! I'll get up, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ White handkerchief ♪\N--I'm up! I'm wide awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Covered in stains, you're\Nthe black handkerchief of happiness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook. Play that one \Nsong--ballad version.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:06:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! That's your favorite, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the one from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here? Go look for your pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are you gonna follow us?\NI bet your mama's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Eat up, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! When did you name him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please help us! He's severely wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, an injured man fell overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss him a life preserver! \NWe'll save him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can swim...\NI guess that's all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! No, no, Laboon.\NDon't wake everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing for you when the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Everyone, sing that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure! We found treasure, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna party today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea monster sighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't go easy on anyone\Nwho picks on Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an option, Laboon.\NPlease hang tight and wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good boy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think like he likes you best, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Laboon loves music!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! The shape of your head\Nmakes him think you're kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you try to reason with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he wasn't willing to listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't strong enough to\Nprotect him from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way we could\Ntake him to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! The music will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we're comrades,\Nbut you're a whale and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line is dangerous! Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could come if you were an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be ferocious beasts unlike\Nanything we've seen in the West Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, listen to--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. He wouldn't listen to a word I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should sing that song for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would have the opposite effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! I know it's hard,\Nbut avoid eye contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not allowed to sing or play your
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ninstruments until Laboon leaves our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sails are about to rip, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder isn't responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the rudder steady! Pull up the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ride the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to the Grand Line \Nawaits us on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, there's light! Light dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The guiding light points\Nto the Grand Line's entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone see Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't seen hide\Nnor hair of him for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for him, but \Nit was for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With any luck, he can return to his pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, are you mentally ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the greatest ocean in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Crocus, the lighthouse keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on crossing Reverse Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Pirates' Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ouch! Don't jinx us, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of the \NRumbar Pirates, Yorkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the West Blue, I've made a bit of a\Nreputation for myself as "Calico" Yorkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Crocus-san, but our ship\Ntook a pretty bad beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to stay as long as you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but provide my meals while you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang! You want to sponge\Noff a bunch of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, cool! Please celebrate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to throw a party today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is the whale\Nthat came with you a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:17:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came with us? That was--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, thank you! This \Nis great! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're injured?! I can't believe\Nyou braved those stormy waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nuts, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Let's sing that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, you sure love that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! It's perfect for pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, you like it too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail leisurely with the sea breeze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail with the waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The setting sun romps about\Non the other side of the tide ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ A ring of birds in the sky sing ♪\N--Crocus-san, would you like to make a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:26.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, you can play anything, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Bid farewell to the port\Nof the weaving village ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ As we set sail, we shall sing heartily ♪\N--Pirates love to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Silver and gold waves \Nturn into ocean spray ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We are off, bound for\Nthe ends of the ocean ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand. You can't\Nrepeat what you did last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that you are simply\Ntoo small to take with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no idea what to \Nexpect from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do you think everyone would do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if harm should come your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't hesitate to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd try, even if that spelled\Nthe end of the Rumbar Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand! I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how hard\Nit was for me last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to travel straight--\Njust straight--across this ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know what, Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly enough, our ship will return\Nto the other side of the Red Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cross the wall again\Nand return to this cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to hang tight\Nfor two or three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll get to see everyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I swear that we will come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By then, you should be big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Later!\N--See ya, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:21:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, let's go on adventures\Ntogether all across the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--Goodbye!\N--Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! We'll now go into the\NGrand Line and travel around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wait for us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Three Years Later"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Florian Triangle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will deliver this. I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It holds the song that Laboon,\Nthe captain, and the rest of us loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised my crewmates\Nthat I would take it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has the choral number of a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performed by the Rumbar Pirates,\Nwho make crying children laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bink's Booze! The Song that\NConnects the Past with the Present!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
